            <section>

					<h1> About Us </h1>

					<p>    Here at Rix, we aim to provide you with the best dining experience in a comfortable, casual and exciting environment. This resulted in wanting a place to share the best times with family and friends while being welcomed by the hospitality you’d come to expect from a fine eatery. We put a lot of great thought & pride into building a space where our guests would feel great to be a part of. We value the importance of knowing the source of our food and trust the ingredients we cook, serve and eat. Products that are raised and harvested locally, in a sustainable manner, will not only taste better, but will also be better for our environment, our health and our future.   </p>

					<p>    [Workers smiling.] </p>

